metadata.name: GhostSoftware CD-ROM #1
metadata.description: GhostSoftware CD-ROM is a limited edition compact disc rewarded to supporters of the GhostSoftware project. It includes ghostly puzzle and card games compatible with the HeavenComputerOS. Legend has it that those who win all the games that come with this CD will have their computers hacked by the ghosts of seven tortured souls. The writing is on the wall.
